      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/node/115" title="Thread safety, singletons and Spring">Thread safety, singletons and Spring</a>
    </h2>
  
  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
          Submitted by Colin Sampaleanu on Tue, 2005-02-01 18:00        </div>
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"> in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_6 first last active"><a href="/presentations" rel="tag" title="A link to a technical article about Spring" class="active">Technical Article</a></li>
</ul></div>
          </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    A <a href="http://erik.jteam.nl/index.php?p=4" target="_self">blog entry</a>
by Erik Wiersma talking about singleton vs. non-singleton beans managed
by Spring, including the case when a singleton needs to deal with a
non-singleton.<br />  </div>

